items.name: NaturallyCoolDetailer_NegV1
items.description:
A negative embedding focused on generating tonally cool images with added detail and realism.

NOTE: Since this focuses on generating cooler tones, you may have to push certain traits. As opposed to "redhead", use "((redhead))" if you are losing that aspect. This also tends to diminish smiles a little, so use weights or brackets to push them further if needed.

Only uses 5 tokens so as not to flood your negative token space.

Images were generated on my upcoming model.

items.name: Carrying person / Princess carry
items.description:
LoRA trained to generate a character carrying another one, usually tagged as "princess carry" in booru tags. I do realize some base models already understand the concept but it is very hard to get it right. This should help those models as well.

Please rate and leave a like if you enjoyed it! And be sure to follow to check out the upcoming models.

Trigger: princess carry

Additional info

I make these models for fun and for the challenge and release them for free for everyone to enjoy, for non-commercial use (see license). The one thing I ask of you is to provide rating and feedback! That helps me understand where I can improve and helps me stay motivated to produce more content! I accept suggestions or requests here or on Civitai discord server.

You can also check my more polished images and upcoming models on my pixiv profile.

This LyCORIS has been trained after carefully selecting 41 images. All photos have been enhanced to make the most of them. I hope you like it!

LyCORIS weights should be between 0.9-1.2

items.name: Reina Kousaka | Hibike! Euphonium
items.description:
You can submit your requests on my discord server!

A weight of ~1.0 is recommended (You might want to adjust the weight depending on your model).
Feel free to experiment with other weights and share your results if you want to!

The main prompt is "Kousaka Reine". Yes I'm aware that there is a typo in there :/
Use "long hair" for her hairstyle.

For her outfits try the following prompts:

Summer Uniform:
"KousakaSummer, long hair, white serafuku, short sleeves, pink neckerchief, blue skirt, black socks, kneehighs, loafers"

Winter Uniform:
"KousakaWinter, long hair, school uniform, brown skirt, brown shirt, long sleeves, black thighhighs, sailor collar, red neckerchief"

Band Uniform:
"KousakaBand, long hair, band uniform, white gloves, shako cap"

Let me know if you have any issues.

Used embeddings for sample pictures:

negative_hand

If you have any feedback or questions just write in the comments or hit me up on reddit or discord.

modelVersions.name: ShenHuaV8
modelVersions.description:
a+b,fantasy world+(lofi+epic)+(zhuzhishanG+aZovyaRPG+no man diffusion+urben)+robotv2+中国风=ShenHuaV8

原名：shenhuav7.1test1945,测试了不计其数配比合并顺序，有很多独具特色样本但作为全能性MODEL并不完美，V8特点实在太多了，和6功能性相比虽然稍弱，然而强在美观和想象力的延展，以及机械表现，ShenHuaV8兼具FTv4,Fantasy world的部分功能，或搭配来用。

modelVersions.name: ShenHuaV7
modelVersions.description: 暂时最终版，a+b:fantasy world+lofiepic50+zhunourben50+robotv2+中国风=Shenhuav7,部分情况下容量可以翻倍，先用大并小，5G多再用小并5G大到7G，再7G并5G到9G。搭配多次失败，暂时最终版有点遗憾不是完全真实，但9G内容出图不错且更加稳定，AI筛选样本游刃有余，不过还是需要更多测试图。

modelVersions.name: ShenhuaV5-ANIME
modelVersions.description: A+B,(刀鞘2+NightSky+EldenRing3+Envy)+(Chosenchinese+Chinese Wedding2.0)=ShenhuaV5,comic or anime.

modelVersions.name: ShenhuaV4-2.8D
modelVersions.description:
2.8D神话版本最好，可以看是V2的完美升级版，4模型合并了神话V1、诡异中式、西幻和5000LORA模型2.2，橙汁有更好表现力，文字成图容易出怪，减少高纬度出2D抽象图的比率。

The 2.8D myth version is the best and can be seen as the perfect version of V2. The 4 models combine ShenhuaV1, chinese weirdness, WestMagic, and megamodel 2.2(5000lora). fruit juice has better expressive power, and text graphics are prone to monster, reducing the ratio of 2D abstract images at high posible.

modelVersions.name: ShenhuaV3-HR
modelVersions.description:
神话V3是基于V2版基础上，与西幻，5000LORA模型，真实v6四拼装合成的，由于真实V6加入现在也可以使用年代服饰，但牺牲了敦煌的一些特点，水中敦煌出图直裸片瓦不带，LORA融合程度和V2版差不多，每个不同维度丧失的功能可以前模型交换着用。

A+B,Four Packs:

ShenhuaV2+Westmagicv10+megamodel4800_21+HRV6=ShenhuaV3

ShenhuaV3 is a realistic fantasy model.ShenhuaV2 is 2.8D,and GuzhuangV1(ShenhuaV1)is 2.5D. They are not which one the best but each one got own features by itself.

modelVersions.name: ShenHuaV2

items.name: Nikaido (Dorohedoro) TI
items.description:
The female protagonist from the anime Dorohedoro. This model does NOT include the art style from the show. Nikaido is a larger sized woman with spikey blonde hair, and bluish green eyes. This model will create that person. Works with any other TI or LoRA, and is compatible with most checkpoints. Clip Skip is not required, but it does make the result look better (in my opinion).

Because her clothes in the show were mostly a green jumpsuit, her clothes tend to end up being green. If not specified in the prompt or negative, her hair will either end up normal or in a ponytail.

Training info:

22 images from the show upscaled to 4k within SD (no birme downscaling)

Images tagged with WD14 Tagger, character traits filtered out

Trained on Google Colab for 10k steps at a rate of .0005 with NAI model

items.name: Volkswagen Beetle (70s model)
items.description:
You can support me here to be able to render better models (https://ko-fi.com/djo226). Supporters can request model.

Exclusive models are also available on my Patreon.

The Volkswagen Beetle—officially the Volkswagen Type 1, is an economy car that was manufactured and marketed by the German company Volkswagen (VW) from 1938 until 2003. It has a rear-engine design with a two-door bodystyle and is intended for five occupants (later, Beetles were restricted to four people in some countries).

Prompt : Beetle, realistic, natural lighting, post-processing, ultra realistic, highly detailed, very detailed, cinematic, hyper realistic, intricate scenery, sharp, photo by Annie Leibovitz, film, studio lighting, detailed skin, ultra realistic, bokeh, sharp features <lora:Beetle:0.8>

Negative prompt: (deformed iris, deformed pupils, semi-realistic, cgi, 3d, render, sketch, cartoon, drawing, anime, mutated hands and fingers:1.4), (deformed, distorted, disfigured:1.3), poorly drawn, bad anatomy, wrong anatomy, extra limb, missing limb, floating limbs, disconnected limbs, mutation, mutated, ugly, disgusting, amputation

Steps: 90, Sampler: DPM++ 2M Karras, CFG scale: 12, Seed: -1, Face restoration: GFPGAN, Size: 768x1024, Model hash: 81086e2b3f, Model: realisticVisionV20_v20

Face restoration is optional, may provide better result if not activated.

Use Beetle as trigger.

New process to get better result :

Set a prompt with a low weight (like <lora:Beetle:0.4>) and the action/situation you want (even with a lower resolution like 512x768, it'll be faster and avoid duplicate). Send the result of your choice to img2img, set the weight to <lora:Beetle:0.8>, set a higher resolution but keep proportion. Enjoy!

items.name: Training Prompt Mega List
items.description:
I made GPT4 generate thousands of prompts I could use for training. Specifically, these wildcards intentionally are not overloaded with super elaborate prompts.

The intent is to use these prompts to generate images and then use these same prompts as caption input to the training data. I feel like using auto-captioning tools like "Interrogate CLIP" often produce garbage, and I don't want to be bothered with cleanup. Going from text to image seems more consistent than image to text, hence these wildcards.

v2.0-sneak-peek: Unsorted subset of upcoming v2.0

v2.0: Used GPT4 through the OpenAI's API. Threw 100 USD at it.

v1.0: Used ChatGPT3.5 and ChatGPT4 manually through a few sessions.

items.name: Yennefer | The Witcher 3 : Wild Hunt
items.description:
Character Lora of Yennefer of Vengerberg from The Witcher 3 : Wild Hunt

"You crossed the wrong sorceress!" -Yennefer

Batman approves her choice of colours -soul3142


This work is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International License.

If you want to, you can support me on Patreon or Buy me Coffee.

My Witcher LoRA Index - soul3142's Guide to the Witcher Universe. additionally you can check out some characters i've made from other games also.

Main Trigger Word - yenW3_soul3142 , check examples for other ones.

RECOMMENDATIONS :-

  1. Highres Fix - must, if you are getting blurry and ugly images

    My upscale method: txt2img 512x768 -> send to img2img -> controlnet tile upscale, tile diffusion 2x scale with 4xUltrasharp upscaler and tiled vae

  2. Weight: 0.6 - 0.8

  3. Clip Skip: 2

  4. Denoising - Don't go too high, it can alter a lot of details

  5. For better face's - you can use ADetailer

I use 0.7 weight, 25 steps, Euler a, Clip skip 2 in nearly all my examples with almost same, simple +ve/-ve prompts regardless of checkpoint for my own consistency purposes.

There are imperfections here & there, which i usually leave it in as is, (i never do any inpainting in examples), most of which like hands can be fixed with better prompting, negative embeddings while other like weapons are just bad majority of the time no matter the model as of today.

Some LoRA's are flexible with any clothing, some are not (usually character's with single costume) so keep these things in mind.

This is an unofficial fanmade LoRA, not intended for any commercial purpose and use. All characters and IP rights are owned by their respective creators and owners. I do not own rights to any of these characters.

items.name: Frank Reynolds (Danny DeVito Always Sunny) Lora
items.description:
Be nice, have fun!

Frank Reynolds is legal father of Dennis and Dee Reynolds, and the majority owner of Paddy's Pub soon after his introduction in season 2 onward. Frank is a millionaire and often funds and enables The Gang's worst schemes and impulses, just to feel a sense of youthfulness and energy. He was once a successful businessman with a long history of illegal operations and dealings with sordid characters, but chooses to abandon that life and redeem himself after leaving his "whore wife", Barbara Reynolds. It is revealed at the end of season 2 that Dennis and Dee are products of an affair and not actually his biological children. He has since embraced his "feral" nature and describes himself as "fringe class". Despite his substantial financial resources, he chooses to share a decrepit studio apartment with Charlie, where they sleep together on a pullout couch and have a surprisingly affectionate pseudo-father/son relationship. The two have similar interests, such as playing the inexplicable game of Night Crawlers and foraging naked in sewers for valuables. He always arms himself with at least one loaded handgun and does not hesitate to brandish or even discharge one when provoked, and often snorts cocaine as part of his daily routine.
